                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-2538-18420822 t18420822-2538-punishment-319"></join>Confined One Year</rs>.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Before Mr. Recorder</hi>.</p>
